margin-left:5.4000pt; padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ; " ><tr><td width=1063  valign=center  style="width:797.8000pt; padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ; " ><p class=p0  style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-autospace:ideograph-other; vertical-align:; " ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >\r\n\r\n</span><span style="font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr><tr><td width=1063  valign=center  style="width:797.8000pt; padding:0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt 0.0000pt ; " ><p class=p0  style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-autospace:ideograph-other; vertical-align:; " ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >\r\n\r\n</span><span style="font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=p0  style="margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-autospace:ideograph-other; " ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >随着5月17日电信日的来临，自从09年初网民对于3G方面关注越来越多，目前国内3G网络主要有中国移动TD-SCDMA，中国联通WCDMA以及&nbsp;中国电信的CDMA2000这三种制式。到底是哪一种网络制式能让消费者满意，相信好多消费者都难以判断。</span><span style="font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >\r\n</span><span style="font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >\r\n而作为3G网络最主要的组&nbsp;成部分-手持终端（手机）&nbsp;，相信也是好多消费者关注的焦点。目前，中国移动TD-SCDMA手机机型频频爆出，其中不乏亮点产品，像联想联想&nbsp;Ophone、诺基亚、多普达&nbsp;Magic等，下面就让笔者与大家一起来了解TD-SCDMA网络制式下的几款强势机型吧。</span><span style="font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >\r\n</span><span style="font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >\r\n诺基亚TD-SCDMA手机　型号：待定　参考报价：尚未上市</span><span style="font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><br>